text=:Category: LinguisticDiscriminationInTheWild%0a:Expansion: Experience of Cantonese vs Mandarin from personal experiences%0a:Author: Spencer_L%0a:Original: [[Articles.DiscriminationAgainstMandarinSpeakers|DiscriminationAgainstMandarinSpeakers]] %0a:OriginalAuthor: [[Profiles.khushiw|khushiw]]%0a:Section: D%0a:Completed: 04.05.2021 - 06:13%0a:Status: complete%0a%0a(:foxform Site.FoxForms#gradeExpansion:)%0a(:foxform Site.FoxForms#gradingcomment:)%0a%0a%0a%25red%25 '''Grading History'''%0a%0a[[#history]]%0a#foxbegin 210505-021051-748510#%0a* [-04.05.2021 - 19:10-] || TA_lili marked as complete%0a#foxend 210505-021051-748510#%0a[[#historyend]]%0a%0a%25red%25 '''Comments to student'''%0a%0a[[#comments]]%0a%0a[[#commentsend]]%0a%0a----%0a----%0a!!%0a%0a%0a----%0a[[#content]]%0a%0aHaving been raised by a parent, whose mother tongue is Cantonese, and another parent, whose mother tongue is Mandarin, I have noticed that there is also discrimination against Cantonese internally and externally. Even though I was exposed to both languages, I am only fluent in Mandarin and can only understand Cantonese to a certain extent. This is mainly due to the fact that my parents prioritized my education my Mandarin over Cantonese, due to the common usage of Mandarin in China. As I have seen from others of Chinese nationality, Cantonese is often noted by them to be loud and exaggerated. This brought me to question such logic, as I was curious how exactly this ideology was created. On main thing that I noticed (note that this may not be true as I am not a fluent Cantonese speaker) is that the extra two tones in Cantonese causes common day expressions to sound very exaggerated. To an extent, such extraneous tones may also have a correlation to being louder. In addition, I have also noticed many ideas that Cantonese is an ugly sounding language in comparison to Mandarin. I would like to note that these are just observations I have heard from others and I do not commit to these statements as facts. If my expansion is ignorant, please let me know and I will revise accordingly.%0a%0a[[#contentends]]%0a----%0a(:Category:)%0a(:GradedBy: TA_lili:)
