diff:1620134035:1620134035:=1,38d0%0a%3c :Category: LinguisticDiscriminationInTheWild%0a%3c :Expansion: Experience of Cantonese vs Mandarin from personal experiences%0a%3c :Author: Spencer_L%0a%3c :Original: [[Articles.DiscriminationAgainstMandarinSpeakers|DiscriminationAgainstMandarinSpeakers]] %0a%3c :OriginalAuthor: [[Profiles.khushiw|khushiw]]%0a%3c :Section: D%0a%3c :Completed: 04.05.2021 - 06:13%0a%3c :Status: ungraded%0a%3c %0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#gradeExpansion:)%0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#gradingcomment:)%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %25red%25 '''Grading History'''%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#history]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#historyend]]%0a%3c %0a%3c %25red%25 '''Comments to student'''%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#comments]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#commentsend]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c !!%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c [[#content]]%0a%3c %0a%3c Having been raised by a parent, whose mother tongue is Cantonese, and another parent, whose mother tongue is Mandarin, I have noticed that there is also discrimination against Cantonese internally and externally. Even though I was exposed to both languages, I am only fluent in Mandarin and can only understand Cantonese to a certain extent. This is mainly due to the fact that my parents prioritized my education my Mandarin over Cantonese, due to the common usage of Mandarin in China. As I have seen from others of Chinese nationality, Cantonese is often noted by them to be loud and exaggerated. This brought me to question such logic, as I was curious how exactly this ideology was created. On main thing that I noticed (note that this may not be true as I am not a fluent Cantonese speaker) is that the extra two tones in Cantonese causes common day expressions to sound very exaggerated. To an extent, such extraneous tones may also have a correlation to being louder. In addition, I have also noticed many ideas that Cantonese is an ugly sounding language in comparison to Mandarin. I would like to note that these are just observations I have heard from others and I do not commit to these statements as facts. If my expansion is ignorant, please let me know and I will revise accordingly.%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c (:Category:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
